sequenceDiagram
  actor U as User
  participant R as Route (TanStack Router)
  participant H as Hook (TanStack Query + useServerFn)
  participant SF as Server Function (createServerFn)
  participant DB as Neon Postgres (Drizzle)

  U->>R: Navigate to page
  R->>H: Render + request data
  H->>SF: Call server function (validated input)
  SF->>SF: Validate + authorize request
  SF->>DB: Run query/mutation
  DB-->>SF: Result rows
  SF-->>H: DTO response
  H-->>R: Cache + provide data
  R-->>U: Render UI / updates

